 MATHEW, KUTTYIL KURIEN MATHEW, KUTTYIL KURIEN VAIDYIALINGAM, C.A.
 
CITATION: 1972 AIR 239 1972 SCR (2) 515 1972 SCC (1) 191 
ACT:
 Compromise decree-Party to decree given time to do an act within a specified period or by a specified day-Party failing to do it on the ground of impossibility of performance on the last day specified-Principles to be applied-Compromise decree, construction of according to law- Does not amount to varying of decree-Decree though in the nature of contract, different consideration apply when embodied in Judge's order.
 
